----------------------------------------------------
Source:   https://zenodo.org/records/10813168 (DOI 10.5281/zenodo.10813168)
License:  CC-BY-4.0 — per the Zenodo record's authoritative metadata grant, the
          deliberately-chosen redistributable release (distinct from the original
          CC-BY-NC-SA records 8208688 / 8360242). NOTE: the data file still embeds
          a stale "# Licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0" header from that original
          release; the record-level CC-BY-4.0 grant governs this redistribution.
Scope:    hg19 (GRCh37) per-variant am_pathogenicity + am_class only (standalone
          `alphamissense.db`), used as a context-only complement to REVEL — never
