Version:  AlphaMissense hg19 predictions, Zenodo record 10813168 (v3, 2023-09-19).
Citation: Cheng, J., Novati, G., Pan, J. et al. "Accurate proteome-wide missense
          variant effect prediction with AlphaMissense." Science 381, eadg7492
