"AlphaMissense" and "Google DeepMind" are used here solely for source attribution.
Yeliztli is an independent project and is not affiliated with or endorsed by
Google DeepMind.

PharmGKB (cross-source pharmacogenomic evidence: LoE + DPWG)
-----------------------------------------------------------
Source:   https://www.pharmgkb.org/ (clinical annotations, guideline annotations,
          drug labels — downloads accessed 2026-06-11)
License:  CC-BY-4.0 ShareAlike (CC-BY-SA 4.0). **ShareAlike honored:** the
          PharmGKB-derived data redistributed here (the PharmGKB Level of Evidence
