          `backend/data/pgx/pgx_guideline_sources.csv`) is itself made available
          under CC-BY-SA 4.0; recipients who reuse it are subject to the same
          license. PharmGKB data is not sold for commercial use.
Scope:    Per-(gene, drug) best PharmGKB Level of Evidence (1A-4) and whether a
          DPWG recommendation exists — context-only evidence layered over CPIC,
          never altering a finding or recommendation.
Citation: Whirl-Carrillo, M., Huddart, R., Gong, L. et al. "An Evidence-Based
          Framework for Evaluating Pharmacogenomics Knowledge for Personalized
          Medicine." Clin. Pharmacol. Ther. 110(3), 563-572 (2021).
          doi:10.1002/cpt.2350 — and cite PharmGKB per
          https://www.pharmgkb.org/page/citingPharmgkb

"PharmGKB" and "DPWG" are used here solely for source attribution. Yeliztli is an
